311
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:14,360
Aduhai. Aduh, sakitnya kepala saya.

312
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:19,920
- Helo.
- Helo.

313
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:23,560
Hei, budak kecil.

314
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,640
Maafkan pak cik.

315
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,680
Pak cik tak boleh turunkan ini!

316
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:32,160
Aduhai. Kamu tak boleh
sewenang-wenangnya tampal poster di sini.

317
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:33,280
Sila ke tepi.

318
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:34,640
Hentikan!

319
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:38,240
- Aduhai. Kuatnya budak ini. Sudahlah.
- Pak cik tak boleh tanggalkannya.

320
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:40,160
Jangan degil. Ke tepi.

321
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,800
[Orang hilang Jeong Yu-na]

322
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:42,360
- Aduhai.
- Hei.

323
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:45,160
- Jangan koyak poster mak saya!
- Sudahlah.

324
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:47,080
Hei, berikan saya itu.

325
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,360
-Helo.
-Terima kasih atas khidmat awak.

326
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:51,440
Baiklah. Apa...

327
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:55,240
Kamu In-seon?

328
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,480
[Kad Pengenalan Penjawat Awam,
Ryu Su-yeol]

329
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:06,000
Betulkah pak cik ini polis?

330
00:19:06,840 --> 00:19:08,960
Jadi, kamu ingat semua polis
nampak seperti samseng?

331
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:11,200
Kamu masih tak percayakan pak cik
walaupun dengan kad pengenalan itu?

332
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,160
Lupakan tentang itu.

333
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,920
Makanlah aiskrim kamu.

334
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:28,680
Kamu tahu… Mengenai mak kamu.

335
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,520
Pak cik

336
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:34,800
